data.description: Current loan rate is 4.75% and it is ASSUMABLE! Welcome home! This property is less than 2 years old and has all of the upgrades you could ask for. Three bedrooms and 2.5 baths are all upstairs leaving plenty of room for your living room and kitchen area. The kitchen has upgraded quartz countertops and upgraded cabinets with modern hardware. The backyard boasts the perfect combination of pavers and turf, perfect for entertaining!! The home has solar with a loan and the buyer can either assume the solar loan or the seller can have them removed. Security system is already installed, this home has it all and it is priced aggressively in today's market. Don't miss this opportunity!!
